SQL_STMT_U.val: select T0.WhsCode, WhsName, isnull(OnHand, 0) as OnHand, isnull(IsCommited, 0) as IsCommited, isnull(OnOrder, 0) as OnOrder, isnull(StockTotal, 0) as TotalStock, isnull(MinStock, 0) as MinStock, isnull(MinOrder, 0) as MinOrder, isnull(AvgPrice, 0) as AvgPrice from OWHS T0 left join ( select WhsCode, ItemCode, OnHand, IsCommited, OnOrder, (isnull(OnHand,0)+isnull(OnOrder,0)-isnull(IsCommited,0)) as StockTotal, MinStock, MinOrder, AvgPrice from OITW where ItemCode=':1' ) T1 on T0.WhsCode=T1.WhsCode order by T1.StockTotal desc, T1.OnHand desc
